pan><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/7/02 4:08:53 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouselaboratory.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2294.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: how many attempts per skill increase?</span><hr size=1> Just been working on this, at slightly lower level.<br><br>Started at 202 skill.  Used 20 stacks of ingredients / attempts (well, 40 stacks of the ivy), got 14 skill raises.<br><br>Also around 50% success rate on average.<br><br>(edit - just tried some more, from a further 6 stacks, only 1 skill raise..., so vaslin's average is looking about right)<br><br>Unless you have a lot of free inventory space there will be a lot of running back and forth if you are not near the vendor, especially if you want to sell back the unstackable poisons.<br><br>Stevo <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ustevostevo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Stevostevo</A> at: 5/7/02 7:04:33 am<br></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouselaboratory.showPrevMessage?topicID=2294.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouselaboratory.showNextMessage?topicID=2294.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouselaboratory.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2294.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouselaboratory.emailToFriend?topicID=2294.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouselaboratory.threadControl?topi